text.tspan: No overcrowding: fewer than 2.5 people per room. Medium overcrowding: more than 2.5 people per room

svg.text: Critical overcrowding: 5 or more people per room

text.tspan: Migrant status is identified by the mother's place of residence at the time of birth.
